{"tid":2355971,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"薛永恒：安心出行下載數字不感滿意","createTime":"2021-01-06T12:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T13:08:37.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"debf377c0fb53ce3252840768bdf85ecf76ea711","tid":2355971,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2021/01/06/2679956_eda034fc8e6359816ac8b2c64deec8fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2021%2F01%2F06%2F2679956_eda034fc8e6359816ac8b2c64deec8fd.jpg&h=c1cbe993&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n薛永恒表示，對「安心出行」下載數字不感滿意。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n創新及科技局局長薛永恒表示，「安心出行」應用程式現時共有43萬人次下載，數字並非令人滿意。<br />\n<br />\n薛永恒強調，「安心出行」是自願參與，希望能有更多市民使用。對於會否強制市民使用程式，他說不會排除任何可能性。<br />\n<br />\n薛永恒稱，目前共有6.7萬個公私營場所參與展示「安心出行」二維碼，包括5.4萬個私營場所。由上月2日至本月4日，執法部門曾對餐飲及表列處所進行8.7萬次巡查，18間餐飲處所因未妥善張貼「安心出行」二維碼而被檢控。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯議員梁志祥建議，當局將電子針卡加入程式。薛永恒稱，協助市民記錄疫苗接種及感染風險通知有關連，會積極研究，但要探討如何在合併後仍能發揮兩者功能。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2679956/%E8%96%9B%E6%B0%B8%E6%81%92%3A%E5%AE%89%E5%BF%83%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%8B%E8%BC%89%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%97%E4%B8%8D%E6%84%9F%E6%BB%BF%E6%84%8F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2679956%2F%25E8%2596%259B%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E6%2581%2592%253A%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25B8%258B%25E8%25BC%2589%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25AD%2597%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E6%2584%258F&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImcF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=36d87988\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2679956/%E8%96%9B%E6%B0%B8%E6%81%92%3A%E5%AE%89%E5%BF%83%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%8B%E8%BC%89%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%97%E4%B8%8D%E6%84%9F%E6%BB%BF%E6%84%8F</a>"},{"pid":"6f0faa08f9b05dbe2598030a5acb7b43f4cca6f6","tid":2355971,"uid":13065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T13:01:46.000Z","msg":"藍絲原來得43萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2053d7c5979e1e4ddd202e24483725cbe80dd96","tid":2355971,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f0faa08f9b05dbe2598030a5acb7b43f4cca6f6","tid":2355971,"uid":13065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T13:01:46.000Z","msg":"藍絲原來得43萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T13:07:56.000Z","msg":"我地輸了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得咁少人參與"},{"pid":"5609b2d6dade01a5604d2c5e35964e300b9b71b9","tid":2355971,"uid":216204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T13:08:37.000Z","msg":"唔下載就拉"}]}